CAL. NUMBERING: "Lwxy.z" → "wx"=year development began, "y"=sequence # in that development year, "z"=variation # (Ex: L043.5 = 3rd movement developed in 2004 & 5th variation of base cal. L043; L901.0 development began 1990)
